Text: Please please please tell me, that you're getting these from somewhere OTHER than DirecTV! I'm thinking I'm gonna need you next week.
I am getting them from a different source :) Did you have any luck in getting Larry Crowne? I'm still keeping my eyes open for a decent souce for you.
Yes, thanks, I did! Ok, good. At least I know I'll be able to keep watching if DirecTV and Fox don't come to terms! Oh, that makes me very happy.
